WEBVTT

00:07.257 --> 00:09.885
Eric and I last fucked
two weeks ago.

00:10.052 --> 00:13.272
<i>We've been involved
since the Solstice Party.</i>

00:13.430 --> 00:15.478
YURI: I found that
where Pettigrew was killed.

00:15.641 --> 00:17.359
Standard Fortitude
police issue.

00:17.518 --> 00:18.735
INGRID: <i>Let me know
where you're calling from.</i>

00:18.894 --> 00:21.238
I don't know.

00:21.396 --> 00:23.114
Don't ever do that to me again,
'cause I do this for you.

00:23.273 --> 00:24.115
SKIPPER:
<i>I take the tusks?</i>

00:24.274 --> 00:25.150
Yeah, they're on board.

00:25.317 --> 00:26.318
I'll take them now.

00:26.485 --> 00:27.782
CARRIE:
<i>Come on, Dad.</i>

00:27.945 --> 00:28.912
<i>We've got to go home.</i>

00:29.071 --> 00:30.994
I'm going to the
mainland in the morning.

00:31.156 --> 00:32.658
I don't want to see
you before I leave.

00:32.824 --> 00:34.997
YURI:
<i>They're all covering for Eric.</i>

00:35.160 --> 00:36.252
They're all in it.

00:36.411 --> 00:37.333
ALLERDYCE:
<i>Shirley?</i>

00:39.790 --> 00:44.045
♪ There in the day, come to me ♪

00:44.211 --> 00:48.091
♪ Straight into my arms ♪

00:50.050 --> 00:51.893
♪ I tried to caress it ♪

00:52.052 --> 00:54.305
<i>♪ Ooh, ooh ♪</i>

00:54.471 --> 00:56.894
♪ But it ran
through my fingers ♪

00:57.057 --> 01:00.903
